#: ../../theme_options.md:8
msgid ""
"Streamlit themes are defined using regular config options: a theme can be"
" set via command line flag when starting your app using streamlit run or "
"by defining it in the [theme] section of a .streamlit/config.toml file. "
"For more information on setting config options, please refer to the "
"Streamlit configuration documentation."
msgstr ""

